com.github.robtimus.filesystems.attribute

Class FileAttributeViewCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.robtimus.filesystems.attribute.FileAttributeViewCollection

  • public final class FileAttributeViewCollection
extends Object
    An immutable collection of file attribute views. Each view is represented as a FileAttributeViewMetadata object. Instances of this class can be used to implement several methods in FileStore, FileSystem and FileSystemProvider.
    Author:
    Rob Spoor
    Since:
    2.2
